---
---

<section id="como-usar">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center">
      <div>
        <span class="kicker kicker-dot">¿Cómo se usa?</span>
        <h2>Así de fácil. En serio.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Exporta, comparte, listo. Sin configuraciones, sin cuenta, sin leer manuales.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-grid">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <article class="how-card">
        <div class="how-gif">
          <span class="how-step">1</span>
          <div class="gif gif-export">
            <div class="chat-window">
              <div class="chat-hd">
                <div class="av"></div>
                <div>La Fábrica de Chocolate</div>
                <div class="dots">⋮</div>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-body">
                <div class="bubble l">Listos para el asado del domingo?</div>
                <div class="bubble r">Yo llevo la carne 👍</div>
                <div class="bubble l">Perfecto!</div>
                <div class="bubble r">Aquí estaré 🔥</div>
                <div class="bubble l">Nos vemos entonces</div>
              </div>
              <div class="menu">
                <div class="menu-item">Ver contacto</div>
                <div class="menu-item">Buscar</div>
                <div class="menu-item">Silenciar</div>
                <div class="menu-item">Más</div>
                <div class="menu-item highlight">📤 Exportar chat</div>
              </div>
              <div class="cursor">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 3l14 7-7 2-2 7-5-16z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="overlay">
                <div class="share-sheet">
                  <div class="title">Compartir con</div>
                  <div class="share-apps">
                    <div class="app">✉️</div>
                    <div class="app">📁</div>
                    <svg class="app g" viewBox="0 0 220 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="220" height="220" rx="48" fill="#0f3d2e"/><circle cx="72" cy="136" r="10" fill="#00d67e"/><path d="M56,174 C56,144 88,144 88,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/><circle cx="148" cy="136" r="10" fill="#00d67e"/><path d="M132,174 C132,144 164,144 164,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/><circle cx="110" cy="128" r="13" fill="#00d67e"/><path d="M85,174 C85,138 135,138 135,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/><path d="M84,42 H170 Q178,42 178,50 V92 Q178,100 170,100 H118 L110,114 L102,100 H84 Q76,100 76,92 V50 Q76,42 84,42 Z" fill="#00d67e"/><polyline points="88,86 110,70 134,76 162,52" fill="none" stroke="#0f3d2e" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="162" cy="52" r="7" fill="#0f3d2e"/></svg>
                    <div class="app">💬</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="gif-progress"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-body">
          <h3>Exporta tu chat</h3>
          <p>En WhatsApp: toca el nombre del grupo → <em>Más</em> → <em>Exportar chat</em> → <em>Sin multimedia</em>. Te da un <code style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--brand)">.zip</code>. Eso es todo.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <article class="how-card">
        <div class="how-gif">
          <span class="how-step">2</span>
          <div class="gif gif-share">
            <div class="file-card">
              <div class="file-icon"></div>
              <div class="file-name">chat.zip</div>
              <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:8px;color:var(--ink-3)">214 KB</div>
            </div>
            <svg class="arrow" style="left:50%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:40px;height:40px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            <div class="app-card">
              <svg class="app-icon" viewBox="0 0 220 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <rect width="220" height="220" rx="48" fill="#0f3d2e"/>
                <circle cx="72" cy="136" r="10" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <path d="M56,174 C56,144 88,144 88,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <circle cx="148" cy="136" r="10" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <path d="M132,174 C132,144 164,144 164,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <circle cx="110" cy="128" r="13" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <path d="M85,174 C85,138 135,138 135,174Z" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <path d="M84,42 H170 Q178,42 178,50 V92 Q178,100 170,100 H118 L110,114 L102,100 H84 Q76,100 76,92 V50 Q76,42 84,42 Z" fill="#00d67e"/>
                <polyline points="88,86 110,70 134,76 162,52" fill="none" stroke="#0f3d2e" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <circle cx="162" cy="52" r="7" fill="#0f3d2e"/>
              </svg>
              <div class="app-name">Grupero</div>
              <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)">Abrir con</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="gif-progress"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-body">
          <h3>Compártelo con Grupero</h3>
          <p>Abre el <code style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--brand)">.zip</code> directamente desde la app. Sin cargas, sin esperas, sin subir nada a ningún servidor.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <article class="how-card">
        <div class="how-gif">
          <span class="how-step">3</span>
          <div class="gif gif-results">
            <div class="dash">
              <div class="dash-hd">
                <div class="dash-title">Fútbol Domingos</div>
                <div class="dash-pill">Analizado</div>
              </div>
              <div class="ring-wrap">
                <div class="ring">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64">
                    <circle class="t" cx="32" cy="32" r="28"/>
                    <circle class="p" cx="32" cy="32" r="28"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="ring-num"><span>87</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="ring-labels">
                  <div class="rlab"><span class="rdot g"></span><b>45</b> activos</div>
                  <div class="rlab"><span class="rdot y"></span><b>8</b> en riesgo</div>
                  <div class="rlab"><span class="rdot r"></span><b>3</b> inactivos</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="insight">
                <svg class="insight-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 9v4M12 17h.01M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/></svg>
                <div><b>3 miembros</b> no asistieron a los últimos 2 eventos</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="gif-progress"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-body">
          <h3>Obtén los resultados</h3>
          <p>La IA analiza patrones de participación, detecta eventos, cuenta asistencias, calcula salud del grupo. Todo en <em>menos de 30 segundos</em>.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
